ss reporter is bound.  \n  \n```\nvoid report(const _ProgressType& val) const;\n```  \n  \n### Parameters  \n `val`  \n The payload to report through a progress notification.  \n  \n## See Also  \n [concurrency Namespace](concurrency-namespace.md)\n"}